00:16:03.140 --> 00:16:05.140
you find that in the midst of the multitudes,

00:16:05.140 --> 00:16:07.300
God is always interested in the individual.

00:16:08.260 --> 00:16:09.780
There was a certain man.

00:16:09.780 --> 00:16:11.500
There was a certain centurion.

00:16:11.500 --> 00:16:13.300
There was a lame man.

00:16:13.300 --> 00:16:15.020
You find the individual,

00:16:15.020 --> 00:16:18.380
