We begin to understand that he offers to Jeremiah,

00:17:20.940 --> 00:17:22.260
call unto me.

00:17:22.260 --> 00:17:25.540
Wow, what an invitation here in James 1.

00:17:25.540 --> 00:17:28.740
What an invitation that James says to these readers

00:17:28.740 --> 00:17:29.820
and to us this morning,

00:17:29.820 --> 00:17:32.380
if any of you lack wisdom, let them ask of God.

