00:18:48.520 --> 00:18:50.240
And we find here this morning

00:18:50.240 --> 00:18:51.800
that there is something for you,

00:18:51.800 --> 00:18:53.640
there is something for me to request.

00:18:53.640 --> 00:18:56.440
When we go through life, when we're facing the trials,

00:18:56.440 --> 00:18:59.480
when we're going day by day, we must acknowledge,

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:02.080
we must recognize that we lack wisdom

00:19:02.080 --> 00:19:04.000
and that God has all wisdom.

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:07.960
And then it leads us to the place of asking God.

00:19:07.960 --> 00:19:09.559
Let him ask.

00:19:09.559 --> 00:19:13.600
Many times, we fail to receive wisdom

00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:15.220
