00:21:44.459 --> 00:21:47.259
That word means bountifully or sufficiently.

00:21:47.259 --> 00:21:50.679
And I'm thankful that God gives wisdom in that manner,

00:21:50.679 --> 00:21:52.979
that he giveth to all men liberally.

00:21:52.979 --> 00:21:56.159
I'm thankful that our God is no respecter of persons.

00:21:56.159 --> 00:21:56.999
Amen.

00:21:56.999 --> 00:22:00.299
I'm thankful that it's all level ground at the cross.

00:22:00.299 --> 00:22:01.339
And the fact of the matter

00:22:01.339 --> 00:22:03.259
