00:22:03.259 --> 00:22:06.179
This truth of James one in verse number five

00:22:06.179 --> 00:22:09.220
is not just for the spiritual leaders.

00:22:09.220 --> 00:22:10.500
It's not just for the pastors.

00:22:10.500 --> 00:22:12.739
It's for every child of God

00:22:12.739 --> 00:22:16.339
that God will give to every man liberally.

00:22:16.339 --> 00:22:19.779
And then it says this, and upbraideth not.

00:22:19.779 --> 00:22:22.839
